Check this out! 😧
The new residential Mega Yacht ‘Somnio’ will be the largest yacht in the world when it launches in 2024.

This 728 feet mansion will have 39 apartments across 6 floors, with apartment prices starting from $11,000,000.
However, it is only possible to purchase by an invitation.
The cost of the project is to be around $600,000,000 and it will be built in Norway.
Photos by @winchdesign_wd 

What are your thoughts about this?👇
#tophomes
